{"tid":952580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國「黃背心」運動爆衝突   交通警員一度拔槍指向衝前示威者","createTime":"2018-12-23T09:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T16:14:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"af829a6ce489a47ca41b666988e8c667ad053d84","tid":952580,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Rhgh65NB/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FRhgh65NB%2Fimage.jpg&h=46e0a863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5c1ea8dbe60383dd580a0c45\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5c1ea8dbe60383dd580a0c45&d=Ne99BDIxKz%2BAP7GrYjwHr9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7e2dba8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5c1ea8dbe60383dd580a0c45</a><br />\n法國連續第六個周末有「黃背心」示威，雖然示威人數大減，但仍有零星衝突，有警員拔槍指向衝前的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n在巴黎有遇襲警察，企圖扶起橫臥地上的電單車時，被示威者投擲雜物，一名警察拔出手槍，指向「黃背心」示威者；但警員仍被雜物擲中，示威者隨後更一起湧前，幾名警察急忙離開。<br />\n<br />\n警方早前以催淚彈和警棍驅趕示威者。當局又關閉凡爾賽宮，防範出現混亂，巴黎逾百人被拘捕。"},{"pid":"a544201e6b16966fafbb0fc941f50d196f7216a1","tid":952580,"uid":64374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef4141996088df899af6c2a8678ceca26b310515","tid":952580,"uid":207846,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"cctvb<br />\n法國：示威者<br />\n香港：暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4623c0f46ed3ffdf246aaf661dac369eeaaea5","tid":952580,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"ef4141996088df899af6c2a8678ceca26b310515","tid":952580,"uid":207846,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"cctvb<br />\n法國：示威者<br />\n香港：暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class